    "intro": "This board publishes the prices we can verify from public sources now. Coverage will be uneven at first: some sources refresh cleanly, some expose prices but block automation, and many local suppliers still require call, text, email, or order-form follow-up. We will add supplier categories as their public prices become repeatable enough to track.",
