      ],
      "note": "Current table data still starts with chain grocery staples. The next expansion should add supplier products from Anson Mills, Marsh Hen Mill, Carolina Plantation Rice, Captain Harry's, Lowcountry Oyster Co., Lowcountry Fungi, Fry Farms, and Whippoorwill Farms SC."
    },
    "methodology": [
      "Each section compares one normalized spec where possible, not every version of an item.",
      "Rankings use the cheapest exact public price we could verify from an official store, market, farm, mill, or supplier page.",
      "Fresh status means the source refreshed automatically; manual means a public supplier price exists but still needs a purpose-built parser; blocked or stale means the last known price is shown while collection improves.",
      "When a supplier publishes contact-only pricing, order-form pricing, or prices hidden behind JavaScript, we track the source but do not guess."
    ],
